Package com.b2international.snowowl.datastore.version

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    INoopPublishManager
    Marker interface for NOOP publish managers.
    IPublishManager
    Service interface for managing the publication process for a concrete terminology.
    ITagConfiguration
    Represents the required information to perform a tagging in the repository.
    ITagService
    Service for creating a new version (tag) in the repository.
    IVersionCollector Deprecated
    - use Request API instead.
    IVersioningManager
    Service interface for collecting unpublished components and publishing them by setting properties on it such as effective time and/or released flag.
    IVersioningService Deprecated
    - use CodeSystemRequests.prepareNewCodeSystemVersion() instead
    NodeDiffFilter
    Represents a filter for NodeDiff instances.
    NodeDiffPredicate
    Predicate working on NodeDiff instances.
    NodeTransformerService
    Service for transforming an arbitrary number of node diffs into a NodeChange.
    VersionCompareExporterService
    Service for exporting the result of a version compare operation.
    VersionCompareService Deprecated
    - reimplement using RevisionIndex
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultNodeDiffFilter
    Default NodeDiffFilter implementation.
    NodeTransformerServiceClientConfigJob
    Job for registering the NodeTransformerService onto the client-side.
    NodeTransformerServiceImpl
    NodeTransformerService service implementation.
    NoopVersioningManager
    Abstract NOOP versioning manager.
    PublishOperationConfiguration
    Configuration for the publication process.
    TagConfigurationBuilder
    Builder for creating tag configuration instances.
    TagServiceClientConfigJob
    Class for registering the ITagService to the client-side.
    VersionCollector Deprecated
    - use Request API instead.
    VersionCompareExporterServiceClientConfigJob
    Job for registering the VersionCompareExporterService onto the client-side.
    VersionCompareServiceClientConfigJob
    Job for registering the VersionCompareService onto the client-side.
    VersioningManager
    Abstract terminology independent component versioning manager implementation.
    VersioningService Deprecated
    - use CodeSystemRequests.prepareNewCodeSystemVersion() instead
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    VersioningManagerBroker
    Broker for all available terminology specific versioning manager instances.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NoChangesException
    Exception indicating that new version cannot be created because no changes has been made since the most recent version.
    NoContentException
    Exception has to be thrown when one tries to create a new version for a terminology where the content is not available.
    VersioningException
    Exception indicating an error for the version operation.
